Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.76,0:00:09.68,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,大家好，我是 Ossy Flawol
Dialogue: 1,0:00:07.76,0:00:09.68,外语,,0,0,0,,Hey everyone, the name's Ossy Flawol.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:13.36,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,传送门系列是一款第一人称解谜游戏，你要利用传送门
Dialogue: 1,0:00:09.68,0:00:13.36,外语,,0,0,0,,The Portal series is a first person puzzle game that involves you utilising Portals  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:18.00,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,解决测试房间的问题。大家都知道这一点。除了各种各样的解谜机制之外，
Dialogue: 1,0:00:13.36,0:00:18.00,外语,,0,0,0,,to solve Test Chambers. Everyone knows this. Alongside its wide variety of puzzle mechanics,  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:22.32,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,传送门最经典的谜题机制之一就是利用重力本身,
Dialogue: 1,0:00:18.00,0:00:22.32,外语,,0,0,0,,one of Portal's most classic puzzle mechanics is the act of utilising gravity itself,  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.32,0:00:25.60,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,通过传送门创建与动量守恒相关的操作，
Dialogue: 1,0:00:22.32,0:00:25.60,外语,,0,0,0,,creating manoeuvres related to the conservation of momentum through Portals,  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:28.78,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,你可以通过一个传送门，并以同样的速度
Dialogue: 1,0:00:25.60,0:00:28.78,外语,,0,0,0,,where you can drop through a Portal, and come speeding out the other end at the same speed to  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:32.72,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,从另一端飞快地跑出来,制造处所谓的“抛出”
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.78,0:00:32.72,外语,,0,0,0,,launch yourself through the air, creating what is known as the iconic 'Flinging'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:36.89,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1336,790)\fad(170,170)}1. 利用动量守恒，通过传送门在空中飞行的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.02,0:00:36.89,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,{\pos(330.667,454)\fad(170,170)}名词
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:36.56,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,这种物理的实现方式要归功于起源引擎的标志性物理特性
Dialogue: 1,0:00:32.72,0:00:36.56,外语,,0,0,0,,This implementation of physics in this manner is thanks to the Source Engine's iconic physics  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:40.64,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,基于Havok的Ipion虚拟物理的引擎，该引擎演变成了VPhysics
Dialogue: 1,0:00:36.56,0:00:40.64,外语,,0,0,0,,engine based off of Havok's Ipion Virtual Physics, which evolved into the VPhysics  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.64,0:00:44.80,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,引进起源中。众所周知，这个物理引擎负责有趣的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:40.64,0:00:44.80,外语,,0,0,0,,Engine once implemented into Source. This physics engine is responsible for the funny  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.80,0:00:49.04,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,布娃娃效果，这个视频的主题 - 传送门的物理特性
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.80,0:00:49.04,外语,,0,0,0,,ragdolls that Source is all well known for, and on topic for this video - Portal's physics.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.04,0:00:52.32,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,为了把一些技术性的东西说清楚，传送门
Dialogue: 1,0:00:49.04,0:00:52.32,外语,,0,0,0,,To get some technical stuff out of the way, the Portals in the portal franchise  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:56.16,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,与VPhysics进行了独特的互动，因为它带来了很多技术性的挑战，
Dialogue: 1,0:00:52.32,0:00:56.16,外语,,0,0,0,,interact uniquely with VPhysics, as it presents a lot of technical challenges,  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.36,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,如果你有兴趣了解，游戏中的开发者评论会解释很多
Dialogue: 1,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.36,外语,,0,0,0,,the developer commentary ingame explains a lot if you're interested in learning the  
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:02.88,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,传送门团队是如何让VPhysics与传送门互动的细枝末节
Dialogue: 1,0:00:59.36,0:01:02.88,外语,,0,0,0,,nitty gritty of how it was like for the Portal team to get VPhysics interacting with Portals  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.88,0:01:07.12,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,传送门背后的一般编程基本上完全改变了
Dialogue: 1,0:01:02.88,0:01:07.12,外语,,0,0,0,,nicely. The general programming behind Portals was basically entirely changed for the sequel  
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.12,0:01:10.80,外语,,0,0,0,,when it was reprogrammed to be better optimised and more stable, allowing for moving portals,  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:10.80,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,它被重新编程为取得更好的优化和更稳定性，允许移动传送门
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:15.20,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,并让像Xbox 360这样的低端硬件能够渲染多达16个传送门
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.80,0:01:15.20,外语,,0,0,0,,and letting lower end hardware like the Xbox 360 be capable of rendering up to 16 portals  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.20,0:01:18.56,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,这是在分屏玩合作游戏时实现的壮举
Dialogue: 1,0:01:15.20,0:01:18.56,外语,,0,0,0,,at once - a feat achieved by playing the Cooperative Campaign in split screen and  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.59,0:01:20.46,中 - 翻译,NOTE,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(932,775)}更正：总共有32个传送门\N（我没有朋友一起玩)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.56,0:01:21.52,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,所有4个传送门都是可见的，并且通过传送门本身有一定程度的递归
Dialogue: 1,0:01:18.56,0:01:21.52,外语,,0,0,0,,having all 4 portals visible and a level of recursion through the Portals themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.52,0:01:23.12,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,所以，现在我们已经澄清了这一点，而且每个人都
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.52,0:01:23.12,外语,,0,0,0,,So, now that we have that cleared up and everyone  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:25.92,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,在同一起点上 - 这是故事真正开始的地方
Dialogue: 1,0:01:23.12,0:01:25.92,外语,,0,0,0,,now on the same page - this is where the story really starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:30.88,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,{\pos(964,958)}2011年6月22日，在一次关于教育和电子游戏如何协同工作的谈话中
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.92,0:01:30.88,外语,,0,0,0,,On the 22nd of June, 2011, during a talk about how education and video games could work in tandem,  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.88,0:01:34.96,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,G胖在2011年的游戏变革节上突然出现，宣布
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.88,0:01:34.96,外语,,0,0,0,,Gabe Newell popped up at the Games For Change Festival of 2011 to announce that Portal 2 would  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:39.44,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,{\pos(952,963.333)}《传送门2》将进入课堂--免费，而且Valve公司正在积极地创建基于《传送门2》的一个课程，
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.96,0:01:39.44,外语,,0,0,0,,be coming to Classrooms - for free, and that Valve was actively working on creating a curriculum that  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.44,0:01:43.76,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,这当然引起了一些人的注意， 当人们
Dialogue: 1,0:01:39.44,0:01:43.76,外语,,0,0,0,,would be based around utilising Portal 2. This certainly raised a few eyebrows, as people were  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.76,0:01:48.56,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,对这可能导致的结果感到好奇时，一年后，在2012年的游戏变革节上，
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.76,0:01:48.56,外语,,0,0,0,,intrigued by what this could lead to, and a year later at the Games For Change Festival for 2012,  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:51.52,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,Valve终于展示了他们正在研究的东西--Steam For Schools
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.56,0:01:51.52,外语,,0,0,0,,Valve finally showed what they were working on - Steam For Schools.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:55.12,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,Valve公司一直在与教育部门的人合作，
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.24,0:01:55.12,外语,,0,0,0,,Valve had been working with people in the educational sector to design a whole  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.12,0:01:57.68,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,围绕《传送门2》和它在课堂上的应用设计整个课程，
Dialogue: 1,0:01:55.12,0:01:57.68,外语,,0,0,0,,curriculum based all around Portal 2 and its application in the classroom,  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.88,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,它的最终结果是创造Steam For Schools，这是一个旨在
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.88,外语,,0,0,0,,and the end result of it came Steam For Schools, being a stripped down version  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.88,0:02:05.28,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,用于学校教育环境的精简版Steam，以及传送门2教育版，
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.88,0:02:05.28,外语,,0,0,0,,of Steam intended to be used in schooling environments, and Portal 2 Educational Version,  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.28,0:02:09.28,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,一个专门的传送门2版本，将被更新和维护，以便在课堂上使用
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.28,0:02:09.28,外语,,0,0,0,,a specialised version of Portal 2 that would be updated and maintained for use in the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.28,0:02:12.64,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,传送门2已经通过Valve的Teach With Portals项目进入了教室，
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.28,0:02:12.64,外语,,0,0,0,,Portal 2 had entered classrooms through Valve's Teach With Portals program,  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.64,0:02:16.40,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,旨在帮助学校和教师在课堂上使用传送门2的计划，
Dialogue: 1,0:02:12.64,0:02:16.40,外语,,0,0,0,,a program designed to help schools and teachers utilise Portal 2 in the classroom  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:20.40,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,通过访问Steam For Schools和提供课程计划来使用，
Dialogue: 1,0:02:16.40,0:02:20.40,外语,,0,0,0,,via giving access to Steam For Schools and providing Lesson Plans to be used, all mostly  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:24.72,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,所有这些都主要围绕着物理和数学科目。我想应该还有一个英语课
Dialogue: 1,0:02:20.40,0:02:24.72,外语,,0,0,0,,focused around the subjects of Physics and Maths. Oh, and a single English lesson plan I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:28.88,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,这些教案读起来相当有趣，工作表和其它所需都有提供，
Dialogue: 1,0:02:25.76,0:02:28.88,外语,,0,0,0,,These lesson plans are pretty interesting to read through, worksheets and all are provided,  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.88,0:02:31.92,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这些底部带有光圈科学标志的东西，
Dialogue: 1,0:02:28.88,0:02:31.92,外语,,0,0,0,,I love how these are all branded with the Aperture Science logo on the bottom,  
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.40,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,这给我带来了一个巨大而愚蠢的微笑，因为试图想象
Dialogue: 1,0:02:31.92,0:02:34.40,外语,,0,0,0,,it brings me a big dumb smile on my face because trying to imagine 
