Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:44.88,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,如果你直接加载，附加内容菜单中的Super 8 Teaser也保持不变
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.12,0:03:44.88,外语,,0,0,0,,if you load directly into it, and the Super 8 Teaser from the Extras menu remains intact.
