Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.88,0:03:58.80,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,然而，教育版真正令人感兴趣的是Puzzlemaker。这个Puzzlemaker
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.88,0:03:58.80,外语,,0,0,0,,The real intrigue for the Educational Version however is the Puzzlemaker. This puzzlemaker  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.44,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,绝对是令人着迷的，因为它是专门为Teach With Portals项目制作的独特版本
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.44,外语,,0,0,0,,is absolutely fascinating due to the fact that it's a unique version made  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:04.64,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,Puzzlemaker包含了三个专门用于Teach With Portals项目的谜题。Puzzlemaker包含三个
