Dialogue: 1,0:04:04.64,0:04:08.24,外语,,0,0,0,,new items - the Contraption Cube, Contraption Button, and Text Bubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:13.76,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,Contraption Cube是一个全新的立方体，专门为教育版制作，
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.96,0:04:13.76,外语,,0,0,0,,The Contraption Cube is an entirely new cube made specifically for the Education Version,  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.76,0:04:17.76,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,独一无二，因为有三个新的选项。你可以在天平上改变立方体的重量，
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.76,0:04:17.76,外语,,0,0,0,,unique for having three new options. You can change the weight of the cube on a scale from  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:21.92,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,从1公斤到80公斤，在5个不同的预设之间改变其摩擦力，
