Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.20,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,并改变其弹性，也是在5种不同的预设之间
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.20,外语,,0,0,0,,and change its elasticity, also between 5 different presets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:29.36,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,根据你设定的重量，Contraption Cube
Dialogue: 1,0:04:26.00,0:04:29.36,外语,,0,0,0,,Depending on the weight you set the cube to, the weight ball inside the Contraption  
