Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.36,0:04:33.20,外语,,0,0,0,,Cube will actually change size to accommodate for it. A cube of 1 kilogram features a tiny  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.20,0:04:36.72,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,一个小小的重量球，而一个最大重量为85公斤的东西，其整个内部
Dialogue: 1,0:04:33.20,0:04:36.72,外语,,0,0,0,,weight ball inside it, while a max weight one at 85 kilograms will have its entire  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:41.12,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,将被重量球所覆盖。这实际上是通过flex group动态完成的，
