Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:09.68,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,默认情况下，Contraption Cube是无摩擦的，这意味着它在任何
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.44,0:05:09.68,外语,,0,0,0,,The Contraption Cube by default is frictionless, meaning it will experience zero drag on any  
