Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.75,0:06:01.36,外语,,0,0,0,,2,100 unique Contraption Cube settings that exist with the customisability of it,  
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.67,0:06:04.05,中 - 翻译,NOTE,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(964.667,429.667)}约2100个潜在的独特装置方块设置
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:05.84,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,使其成为《传送门2》中最多样化的官方测试元素，恭喜Contraption Cube!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.36,0:06:05.84,外语,,0,0,0,,making it Portal 2's most diverse official Testing Element, congratulations Contraption Cube!
Comment: 0,0:06:05.84,0:06:06.40,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,遗憾的是，Contraption Cube无法被涂上凝胶
