Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:18.40,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,这里有一个修复的Contraption Button实际是什么样子的。这个
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.40,0:06:18.40,外语,,0,0,0,,Here's a restoration of what the Contraption Button is actually meant to look like. This  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:22.56,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,按钮如果使用的话是完全不起作用的，由于我们不知道《传送门2》
Dialogue: 1,0:06:18.40,0:06:22.56,外语,,0,0,0,,button is entirely non-functional if used, and due to us not knowing what's going on internally  
