Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:29.76,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,只知道它很可能是和Contraption Cube一起使用的。
Dialogue: 1,0:06:25.84,0:06:29.76,外语,,0,0,0,,do other than the fact it was very likely to be used in conjunction with the Contraption Cube. And  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:34.32,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,是的--如果你想说Contraption Cube在正常的按钮上也能工作，那么它就不能
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.76,0:06:34.32,外语,,0,0,0,,yes - the Contraption Cube works on normal buttons too if you're about to suggest that it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:38.80,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,教育版还为puzzlemaker增加了一个新项目--这就是Text Bubble 
Dialogue: 1,0:06:34.32,0:06:38.80,外语,,0,0,0,,The Educational Version also adds one more new item to the puzzlemaker - This is the Text Bubble,  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:42.72,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,也被称为 "Text Node"。这并不完全是一个宇宙中的测试元素，
Dialogue: 1,0:06:38.80,0:06:42.72,外语,,0,0,0,,also known as a Text Node. This is not exactly an in-universe test element,  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.72,0:06:47.92,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,更多的是它是在关卡中留下注释的一种方式。 你可以在其中写下文字，然后 "播放 "这些文字 
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.72,0:06:47.92,外语,,0,0,0,,more that it is a way to leave notes in the level. You can write text in it and then “play” the text  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.92,0:06:52.00,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,{\pos(981.333,961)}在游戏中，就像你玩一个评论节点一样，文本出现的方式类似于字幕
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.92,0:06:52.00,外语,,0,0,0,,ingame like you would play a Commentary Node, the text appears in a similar fashion to how subtitles  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.00,0:06:56.40,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,在屏幕上的格式，总共最多只有6行，
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.00,0:06:56.40,外语,,0,0,0,,are formatted on your screen, and have a maximum of 6 lines total before the text bubble will just  
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.40,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,在文本气泡直接拒绝显示任何进一步的内容之前，评论节点
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.40,0:07:00.40,外语,,0,0,0,,outright refuse to display anything further. One main difference between Commentary Nodes  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:04.24,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,和文本气泡之间的一个主要区别是，你必须在文本气泡的附近才能激活它，
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.40,0:07:04.24,外语,,0,0,0,,and Text Bubbles is that you have to be in the vicinity of the Text Bubble to activate it, while  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:07.68,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,而评论节点基本上可以从任何地方激活，只要你看着它
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.24,0:07:07.68,外语,,0,0,0,,Commentary Nodes can be activated from basically anywhere so long as you are looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:10.88,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,在我们进一步讨论游戏中的变化之前，我想提及
Dialogue: 1,0:07:07.68,0:07:10.88,外语,,0,0,0,,Before we move onto further ingame changes, I'd like to mention an interesting  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:13.92,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,教育版的puzzlemaker中跳板的一个有趣的特殊性
Dialogue: 1,0:07:10.88,0:07:13.92,外语,,0,0,0,,peculiarity with Aerial Faith Plates in the Educational Edition's puzzlemaker.  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:19.36,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,Valve增加了一个使用 "impulses "的选项，因此，与其简单地放置一个目标
Dialogue: 1,0:07:14.56,0:07:19.36,外语,,0,0,0,,Valve added an option to use ‘impulses', so rather than simply placing a target for the Faith Plate  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.36,0:07:23.84,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,让跳板射向你，不如调整跳板发射物体的力度和角度，
Dialogue: 1,0:07:19.36,0:07:23.84,外语,,0,0,0,,to shoot you towards, you adjust the force and angle that the Faith Plate will launch objects at,  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:29.40,中 - 翻译,NOTE,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(1351.334,376.334)}这有点类似于你在Hammer中设置跳板的方式，\N但不完全是，因为你仍然要在Hammer中设置一个目标
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:29.20,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,分别以牛顿和度数衡量。调节时，水平仪中没有目标点，
Dialogue: 1,0:07:24.48,0:07:29.20,外语,,0,0,0,,measured in newtons and degrees respectively. No target spot is made in the level when compiled,  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.44,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,据推测，这是由于跳板的这一
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.20,0:07:31.44,外语,,0,0,0,,presumably this was due to the fact that this specific new  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.44,0:07:34.32,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,特定新功能是为了在物理课上使用
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.44,0:07:34.32,外语,,0,0,0,,feature of Faith Plates was made to be used in physics classes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:37.52,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,现在我们已经进入游戏，教育版增加了两个新的机制，
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.32,0:07:37.52,外语,,0,0,0,,Now that we're ingame, the Educational Version adds two new mechanics made to  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.52,0:07:40.56,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,是为了在我们要看的学习环境中使用。通过在选项中启用
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.52,0:07:40.56,外语,,0,0,0,,be used in the learning environment that we're going to be looking at. By enabling  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:45.20,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,教育模式，我们可以获得一个秒表和物理学速度操纵器。   
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.56,0:07:45.20,外语,,0,0,0,,Education Mode in the options, we gain access to a stopwatch and physics speed manipulator.  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.20,0:07:50.72,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,按J键，启动秒表计时器，K键停止计时器，L键复位，6键
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.20,0:07:50.72,外语,,0,0,0,,By pressing J, we start the Stopwatch Timer, K to stop the timer, L to reset it, and 6 to toggle  
