Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.72,0:07:54.56,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,在开和关之间切换，如果你在学校做过任何形式的物理学相关实验，
Dialogue: 1,0:07:50.72,0:07:54.56,外语,,0,0,0,,it between on and off, if you've ever done any form of physics related experiments in school,  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:58.64,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,你会知道计时是非常重要的，你几乎肯定使用秒表为物体计时，
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.56,0:07:58.64,外语,,0,0,0,,{\fscx83\fscy95}you'd know that timing is very important and you almost certainly used a stopwatch to time objects,  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:02.72,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,传送门2的教育版用它自己的秒表做了这件事，
Dialogue: 1,0:07:59.28,0:08:02.72,外语,,0,0,0,,Portal 2's Educational Version does this exact thing with it's own stopwatch, and it's  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:06.00,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,而且它实际上是相当不错的。很快就跳回了益智游戏机。  快速跳回Puzzlemaker，
Dialogue: 1,0:08:02.72,0:08:06.00,外语,,0,0,0,,actually rather fascinating. Hopping back to the Puzzlemaker real quick,  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:09.36,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,所有的按钮实际上都有一个 "切换秒表 "的选项，
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.00,0:08:09.36,外语,,0,0,0,,all buttons actually feature a “Toggle Stopwatch” option that will run the  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:13.12,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,只要它们被按下就会运行秒表，你真的可以看出
Dialogue: 1,0:08:09.36,0:08:13.12,外语,,0,0,0,,stopwatch for as long as they're pressed down, you can really tell the level of thought that  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:17.84,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,开发教育版的思想水平，无论如何，回到游戏中......
Dialogue: 1,0:08:13.12,0:08:17.84,外语,,0,0,0,,went into developing the Educational Version with neat quirks like that, anyways, back ingame…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:21.76,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,传送门2教育版最后带来的是前面提到的
Dialogue: 1,0:08:17.84,0:08:21.76,外语,,0,0,0,,The final thing that Portal 2 Educational Version brings to the table is the aforementioned Physics  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.76,0:08:25.84,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,速度操纵器，这基本上是一个更方便的phys_timescale
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.76,0:08:25.84,外语,,0,0,0,,Speed Manipulator, this is essentially a more user-friendly version of the phys_timescale  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:29.84,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,的命令的版本。它可以改变游戏里的物理速度，而且不影响玩家
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.84,0:08:29.84,外语,,0,0,0,,command. It changes how fast physics in the world reacts, and doesn't affect the player.  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:35.83,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,按1设置为100%的速度，2设置为0%，3设置为50%，4设置为10%，
Dialogue: 1,0:08:29.84,0:08:35.83,外语,,0,0,0,,Pressing 1 sets it to 100% speed, 2 sets it to 0%, 3 sets it to 50%, 4 to 10%  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:39.84,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,5设置为1%。你可以用它来确保一旦
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.84,0:08:39.84,外语,,0,0,0,,and 5 sets it to 1%. You can use this to basically ensure objects will drop  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:42.24,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,物体可能停留的平台被移除，物体将在同一时间下降
Dialogue: 1,0:08:39.84,0:08:42.24,外语,,0,0,0,,at the same time once the platform they may be resting on is removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:45.44,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,我对这个东西玩得很开心，用人们无法想象的方式把方块发射出去，
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.24,0:08:45.44,外语,,0,0,0,,I had a lot of fun actually playing around with this thing, launching cubes around in humanly  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.44,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,把物理速度设置为零来停止时间，基本上是把方块
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.44,0:08:49.44,外语,,0,0,0,,impossible ways, setting the physics speed to zero to stop time and essentially sending cubes  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:52.72,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,通过无限循环的抛掷来建立速度。如果有人重新制作基本游戏《传送门2》的用户界面，
Dialogue: 1,0:08:49.44,0:08:52.72,外语,,0,0,0,,through an infinite loop of flings to build up speed. You could probably make a cool mod  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.72,0:08:56.56,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,你也许可以用这个概念制作一个很酷的mod，
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.72,0:08:56.56,外语,,0,0,0,,concept out of this if anyone recreated the UI in base game Portal 2 honestly,  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.56,0:09:01.65,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,我甚至用暂停物理的想法做了一个快速的解谜，让我展示一下
Dialogue: 1,0:08:56.56,0:09:01.65,外语,,0,0,0,,I even made a quick puzzle with the idea of being able to pause physics, lemme show it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.80,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,很完美，不是吗？
Dialogue: 1,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.80,外语,,0,0,0,,Pretty neat isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.12,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,我想我们就快结束这段视频了，
Dialogue: 1,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.12,外语,,0,0,0,,I think we're just about getting close to wrapping up this video,  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:40.80,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,但在我们完全结束之前--教育版为我们准备了最后一个惊喜
Dialogue: 1,0:09:37.12,0:09:40.80,外语,,0,0,0,,but before we fully end it - Educational Version has one final surprise for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.36,0:09:46.56,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,按住R键，我们就可以看到传送门2未使用的反馈平移菜单，
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.36,0:09:46.56,外语,,0,0,0,,By holding down R, we get a proper peek at Portal 2's unused Feedback Ping Menu,  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:49.92,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,这是为Puzzlemaker计划的一个游戏测试系统，原本是
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.56,0:09:49.92,外语,,0,0,0,,this was planned for the Puzzlemaker with the idea of a Playtest system that was originally going  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:53.60,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,要让Puzzlemaker通过整个系统来获得游戏测试的反馈，
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.92,0:09:53.60,外语,,0,0,0,,to be used by puzzle creators to get playtest feedback on their puzzles through a whole system  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:58.80,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,但这是另一个视频的故事。这个反馈平移菜单基本上
Dialogue: 1,0:09:53.60,0:09:58.80,外语,,0,0,0,,that was canned, but that's a story for another video. This Feedback Ping Menu basically acts  
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:02.72,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,与平移工具的作用相同，你可以突出显示对象，选择特定的平移反应
Dialogue: 1,0:09:58.80,0:10:02.72,外语,,0,0,0,,the same as the Ping Tool, you can highlight objects, choose specific ping responses,  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:08.16,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,整个作品为什么在教育版中重新启用了这一功能......谁也不知道，真的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:02.72,0:10:08.16,外语,,0,0,0,,the whole works. Why the hell this was reenabled in Educational Version is… anyone's guess really.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.76,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,当然，我还可以谈更多，教育版似乎
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.16,0:10:11.76,外语,,0,0,0,,There's certainly more I could've talked about, the Educational Version seems like it has its  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.76,0:10:16.64,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,有它自己的一堆未使用的、报废的和丢失的内容，但这是我仍在挖掘的东西
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.76,0:10:16.64,外语,,0,0,0,,own heap of unused, scrapped and lost content but that's something I'm still digging into,  
