Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:20.16,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,另外，我还没打算用这些事实来使这段视频过于复杂化，
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.64,0:10:20.16,外语,,0,0,0,,plus I didn't plan on overcomplicating this video with those facts just yet, this is a  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.16,0:10:23.68,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,这段视频主要是让人们了解《传送门2》的教育版是什么样的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.16,0:10:23.68,外语,,0,0,0,,video to mainly getting people informed about what Portal 2's Educational Version was like,  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:27.12,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,这对我个人来说当然是一种宣泄，因为我记得在我年轻的时候
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.68,0:10:27.12,外语,,0,0,0,,it's certainly cathartic for me personally since I remember trying to campaign for my  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.24,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,曾试图为我的学校争取使用传送门教学项目，因为我认为
Dialogue: 1,0:10:27.12,0:10:30.24,外语,,0,0,0,,school to use the Teach With Portals program when I was younger just because I thought the  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:34.64,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,在学校使用传送门2学习是如此的酷。过了这么久
Dialogue: 1,0:10:30.24,0:10:34.64,外语,,0,0,0,,possibility of using Portal 2 in school and for learning was so cool. Actually playing  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.64,0:10:38.72,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,才玩这个版本的游戏，对我个人来说是非常有成就感的
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.64,0:10:38.72,外语,,0,0,0,,this version of the game after so long is so god damned fulfilling to me personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:41.92,中 - 翻译,,0,0,0,,这就是我今天的全部内容，在推特上关注我，
